text: Fritz Richard Gustav Schuft was a gymnast from Germany. Fritz competed at the 1896 Summer Olympics. He was born on 16 June 1876 and died on 8 February 1948.Gustav Schuft ==References== == Other websites == * Category:1876 births Category:1948 deaths Category:German gymnasts Category:Olympic gold medalists for Germany Category:Sportspeople from Berlin
